24/11/2005
PRISTINA, Kosovo, Serbia-Montenegro -- The OSCE Mission in Kosovo presented guidelines Wednesday (23 November) for police and media in the province, aimed at providing a better understanding of rights and responsibilities of each of them.
The guidelines are based on Kosovo's Provisional Criminal Code, the Juvenile Justice Code and European and international conventions.
The OSCE plans to hold meetings with police and media representatives across the province.
(OSCE Web site - 23/11/05)
